    <warning xml:id="warning-windows-network-shares">
        <indexterm>
            <primary>network shares</primary>
        </indexterm>
        <indexterm>
            <primary>shared drives</primary>
        </indexterm>
        <indexterm>
            <primary>file sources</primary>
            <secondary>on network shares</secondary>
        </indexterm>
        <indexterm>
            <primary>log files</primary>
            <secondary>on network shares</secondary>
        </indexterm>
        <para>Files used as file sources must reside locally on the host the &agentabbrev; application is running on. Files located on network shares are not supported, because the &agent; application is running as a local service and does not have the privileges to access network shares.</para>
    </warning>
